OL,3,CCotherstone residents transform Old
OL,4,CChapel into thriving community business
OL,6,FMore than 1,000 cups of coffee, 600
OL,7,Fpots of tea, 500 breakfast buns and
OL,8,Fcountless slices of homemade cake have
OL,9,Fbeen served in a community-run shop,
OL,10,Fcafe and heritage centre in its first
OL,11,Fmonth.
OL,13,FOne resident told ITV News Tyne Tees:
OL,14,F"It's been a great pleasure for
OL,15,Fbringing the community together.
OL,17,F"It's just a great venue for locals to
OL,18,Fmeet and to bring friends and family."
