OL,3,CCotherstone residents transform Old
OL,4,CChapel into thriving community business
OL,6,FThe project has provided jobs for 12
OL,7,Flocal young people, served more than
OL,8,F2,500 customers, raised #300 for local
OL,9,Fcauses by selling ice creams and
OL,10,Fprovided more than 200 hours of
OL,11,Fvolunteering opportunities since it
OL,12,Fopened in June.
OL,14,FChris Tarpey, from the Project, said
OL,15,Fthey wanted to maintain the aesthetic
OL,16,Ffeel of the chapel, building on the
OL,17,Fheritage of the village.
