OL,3,CCotherstone residents transform Old
OL,4,CChapel into thriving community business
OL,6,FAccording to Plunkett UK, a charity
OL,7,Fthat supports rural communities in
OL,8,Fstarting businesses, #55m has been
OL,9,Finvested in starting up 787 community
OL,10,Fowned businesses across the UK,
OL,11,Fincluding 32 that opened just last
OL,12,Fyear.
OL,14,FThe Old Chapel opened this summer,
OL,15,Ffollowing years of hard work and
OL,16,Ffundraising by the community, which
OL,17,Fraised #150,000 towards the project.
