OL,3,CCotherstone residents transform Old
OL,4,CChapel into thriving community business
OL,6,FThis was boosted by a #120,000 grant
OL,7,Ffrom Durham County Council's Towns and
OL,8,FVillages Community Resilience Fund;
OL,9,F#40,000 from Teesdale Area Action
OL,10,FPartnership's Towns and Villages Fund;
OL,11,Fand a total of #20,000 from Cllr
OL,12,FRichard Bell and Cllr Ted Henderson's
OL,13,Fneighbourhood budgets.
OL,15,FDeputy Leader of Durham County
OL,16,FCouncil, Cllr Richard Bell, said:
OL,17,F"People thought, what do we actually
OL,18,Fneed? The shop is closed. The chapel
OL,19,Fis closed.
