OL,6,F"We need a place where people can
OL,7,Fmeet, socialise, buy the basic
OL,8,Fgroceries and have an asset that
OL,9,Fbrings the community together and it
OL,10,Fthink it's been great the way people
OL,11,Fhave recognised that, and rather than
OL,12,Fjust moan about the loss of something,
OL,13,Fthey've actually got up and done
OL,14,Fsomething about it."
